info.title: Extract Table - DocumentDev
info.description: Extract information from PDF Tables instantly. Using the power of Artificial Intelligence and NLP.
info.x-long-description: At Document.dev we are passionate about teaching computers how to read. We use the latest in open source technologies coupled with proprietary algorithms and data sets to provide the best in the world data extraction capabilities. Use this api to  extract information from PDF Tables instantly. Using the power of Artificial Intelligence and NLP.

parameters.name: Pages
parameters.description:
By default only the first page of the PDF is processed. To process multiple pages pass the desired page count in as a parameter.

Notes:

- Maximum 10 pages can be processed per request

- Accepted input is a number greater than 1 and less than or equal to 10
- Accepted input is the string "all" representing all pages in the PDF up to 10

post.description:
This endpoint accepts a pdf file as a binary payload and returns a JSON containing all tables found within the PDF. By default only the first page is processed. If you would like to process multiple pages pass the "Pages" header to indicate how many.

Notes:
- The table should have unique keys for each row otherwise they will be overwritten in order as per JSON standard
- Currently processes each page independently. Multi page tables will be supported soon.
- Max PDF size is 10MB
